item.description:
The 17th Annual Women's Night of Comedy will feature three women comedians as well as wonderful dinner prepared by the Log Cabin. Be prepared to laugh!

Top 5 Reasons Why You Don't Want
To Miss This Year's Women's Night of Comedy:

1. See and be seen - Great networking opportunities with other local business women

2. Start your weekend early - Go out for a night with the girls one night early

3. Help the community - Proceeds go to help local charitable organizations

4. Be a winner - You don't need to go to the casino to win big, we're giving away cash and prizes

5. Be part of something bigger - Support the Women Business Owner's Alliance's mission to help women rise in business

Stay updated on the event by going to http://wboa.org/comed...
Tickets are available for purchase on the WBOA website. Tickets are available at an early bird price of $44 until January 31, 2010.
